{"tid":1404591,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線，裝修佬入]鐵馬新set up法","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:12:01.000Z","uid":121040,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3fe1202736cdaffff12640ad8472b0bf3ea7af","tid":1404591,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"其實我地係咪可以改良下依家既傳統三角馬陣？<br />\n尋晚有個師兄建議可以咁做<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFw7cRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFw7cRC.jpg&h=4e3d4959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四隻顏色代表四隻馬<br />\n個原理好似老鼠夾咁，一拆黑色上面個三隻馬就會冧落黎同埋高身既設計，如果加返多少cover上去保護性更高<br />\n<br />\n但係前線你地點睇，如果咁樣set會唔會阻住你地做野？因為缺點係set好左既話除非拆左佢否則好難拎得走"},{"pid":"30b79deb9ec07142594ad4ba11caa1395c3b3228","tid":1404591,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7af2085ab62b30aa9c50cf4c50c30aa7256e0134","tid":1404591,"uid":148165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c288f2c22d794dfd3deb20a5a320f5cd57feb7e6","tid":1404591,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不死守<br />\n<br />\n有狗佈防即刻走<br />\n<br />\n轉場再撚狗<br />\n<br />\n撚完散水走</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2c3564d0d280d0c452da7b0756799f1a8b934291","tid":1404591,"uid":40286,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VB3vH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VB3vH3.png&h=cbb99be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴晚係有手足做到 幾好<br />\n<br />\n但長期街頭抗爭對政權影響唔到分毫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ce73179c2002ebf9d83ba5f0e6e67229a1a23d4","tid":1404591,"uid":51677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔難拎走<br />\n將佢打返橫咁擺 <br />\n都係照平時咁推"},{"pid":"536e1d35f2202eddf121f6869c0fb01ec2005dd1","tid":1404591,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f9516ddbf19d03bc102880ac082cef507886cfcd","tid":1404591,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce73179c2002ebf9d83ba5f0e6e67229a1a23d4","tid":1404591,"uid":51677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔難拎走<br />\n將佢打返橫咁擺 <br />\n都係照平時咁推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"大家唔嫌重就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個真係可以考慮下以後咁set"},{"pid":"d6199a7f723a3861e0b7df183304f9600dd962e9","tid":1404591,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b78d2286b51a321d67172ca4af22b2210fd2b21","tid":1404591,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"如果個尾長少少同冇咁斜，一踏上去索帶一斷會夾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461821dc913d0b8a326b4f674f78f4d3851667aa","tid":1404591,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"有創意及有加強防禦效果。"},{"pid":"c91436bf192daaa5dfe1700123bedbce95357864","tid":1404591,"uid":121040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b78d2286b51a321d67172ca4af22b221